{"tid":720632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女警4度高買判感化　官勸勿在工作地搞男女關係  06月28日(四) 11:33   ","createTime":"2018-06-28T05:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T08:49:22.000Z","uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed824b7aed1ae2f5e3d8f8c0b522a11c92c21d72","tid":720632,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:16:15.000Z","msg":"女警4度高買判感化　官勸勿在工作地搞男女關係<br />\n<br />\n06月28日(四) 11:33<br />\n<br />\n年輕女警涉嫌於1個月內先後在3間萬寧連鎖店4度偷取護膚產品，總值逾1.3萬港元，她事後被捕並控以4項盜竊罪名。其代表律師早前求情曾辯稱，被告加入警隊後深受男同袍歡迎，影響工作，她甚至遭上級訓示要和男同袍保持距離，備受壓力下終以身試法。被告李慧玲早前承認4項控罪，今(28日)在九龍城法院被判12個月感化，另須賠償4317港元。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，被告同意感化及社會服務令報告，但基於她的精神狀況，感化官不建議其做社會服務。被告願意遵守感化令，也願意賠償並向受害人公司致歉，<span style=\"color: red;\">她不能再做警察，打算重操故業從事寵物訓練工作</span>，並承諾會珍惜將來。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指，被告認為因與男同事的關係而遭上司針對，縱然當中或有誤解，但其行為必須正直，不應該在工作地方搞男女關係，尊重工作。裁判官指被告或在無意間透過身體語言發出錯誤訊息，令男上司和男同袍產生誤會，上司是否誤解她，她其實心理有數。裁判官自言並非怪責被告，但提醒她要檢點行為，若她再犯必然判監。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180628/mobile/bkn-20180628113304718-0628_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180628%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180628113304718-0628_00822_001.html&d=biwqld0qdl1yqvFOcMZWBTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c8bd8fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180628/mobile/bkn-20180628113304718-0628_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"eadcb6fae3b9ebfdf8891bc9d835a42e2480ccbc","tid":720632,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"李慧玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69680024c23e9d14eda5b50a04df12f9b1c38693","tid":720632,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"你地無做錯到"},{"pid":"5ad5c3803cd999aa7f760da4cfd59ef07b573769","tid":720632,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:21:29.000Z","msg":"即係收兵臭雞啦"},{"pid":"ec1216ebf10294b1242fb53597a8c3f3157de9ad","tid":720632,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:24:00.000Z","msg":"Madam偷野唔使你教"},{"pid":"134b3e2656ce1df7ddeadaeba608149540ea0849","tid":720632,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"她不能再做警察，打算重操故業從事寵物訓練工作<br />\n<br />\n狗訓練狗？"},{"pid":"ab2e69e444365b8da07f8d63bf62540fb8abfc13","tid":720632,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"1953c9d70b78236bd9e5c4072eab07396814ad33","tid":720632,"uid":37708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:08:09.000Z","msg":"一睇就知用西收兵,至少百人斬"},{"pid":"576c71932cac3aa854fc4a2fd3cdc794646ebfb4","tid":720632,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:28:35.000Z","msg":"感化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec35eaf037f289d036530a74097aa081382ea754","tid":720632,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eadcb6fae3b9ebfdf8891bc9d835a42e2480ccbc","tid":720632,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"李慧玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:30:42.000Z","msg":"大口"},{"pid":"266e090795f7ec68d404b6587d7658a85ee74972","tid":720632,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:49:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被告加入警隊後深受男同袍歡迎，影響工作，她甚至遭上級訓示要和男同袍保持距離，備受壓力下終以身試法。<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n照咁講d女模特兒應該全部偷過野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}